<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Account Suspended - FinalsRS</title>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;600;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/output.css" />
    <style>
      body {
        background-color: #111;
        color: #eee;
        font-family: "Inter", sans-serif;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        height: 100vh;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .container {
        text-align: center;
        background: #1a1a1a;
        padding: 3rem;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        max-width: 500px;
        width: 90%;
        border: 1px solid #333;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #ff4444;
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      p {
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: #ccc;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .reason-box {
        background: #252525;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
        border-left: 4px solid #ff4444;
        text-align: left;
      }
      .reason-label {
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #888;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        display: block;
      }
      .reason-text {
        color: #fff;
        font-weight: 500;
      }
      .support-link {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 1rem;
        color: #888;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
      }
      .support-link:hover {
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Account Suspended</h1>
      <p>Your account has been suspended from accessing this service.</p>

      <div class="reason-box">
        <span class="reason-label">Reason</span>
        <div class="reason-text"><%= reason %></div>
      </div>

      <p>If you believe this is a mistake, please contact support.</p>

      <a href="/" class="support-link">Return to Home</a>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
